node.text: Lots of people asked if I’d ever be in @AlphaBetasShow after the pilot released, so I’m excited to announce that I will be in 2022! They’re making a series thanks to everyone’s support on Kickstarter. Support the show to get more episodes and rewards by clicking on the link in my bio!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Moo on June 29, 2021. May be a cartoon of toy.

node.text: Since @youtooz thought it’d be funny to ship out Early Bird last(cruel joke imo), does that mean I’m the only one with a complete set right now?
